<p>When your Mac won&#8217;t boot, Dave and John have some of the answers! This week&#8217;s show finds our hosts talking through all they steps they would take to revive a sick Mac, including different troubleshooting utilities, tips and tricks, plus where to send it when all else fails.</p>
